public static class AuthorizationRegistry.AccessAuthorizationList<T> extends RegistrationList<T>
Class for access and iteration of AccessAuthorizations. Most of the capability is provided through extension of RegistrationList, which requires select overrides to ensure the correct types are built and returned by the iterator.
